\id JOL - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020
\h Joel
\toc1 Joel
\toc2 Joel
\toc3 Joe
\mt1 Joel
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Wach Jehova Nyasaye mane obiro ne Joel wuod Pethuel.
\b
\s1 Bonyo omonjo piny
\q1 
\v 2 Winjuru ma, un jodongo;
\q2 chikuru itu, un duto ma udak e piny.
\q1 Bende gima chalo kama osetimore e ndalou,
\q2 kata e ndalo mag kwereu?
\q1 
\v 3 Nyis nyithindu wachni,
\q2 kendo nyithindu onyis nyithindgi,
\q2 kendo nyithindgi bende onyis tiengʼ maluwogi.
\q1 
\v 4 Gik ma mony mar bonyo oweyo,
\q2 bonyo madongo osechamo;
\q1 gik ma bonyo madongo oweyo
\q2 bonyo matindo osechamo,
\q1 gik ma bonyo matindo oweyo
\q2 bonyo mamoko nochamo.
\b
\q1 
\v 5 Un jomer, chiewuru kendo ywaguru!
\q2 Gouru nduru, un duto ma jomath mag divai;
\q1 gouru nduru nikech divai manyien,
\q2 nikech oseyudhe ogole e dhou.
\q1 
\v 6 Oganda moro osemonjo pinya, en oganda maratego
\q2 kendo gingʼeny mokadho akwana;
\q1 en gi leke mag sibuor madichwo,
\q2 leke mager mag sibuor madhako.
\q1 
\v 7 Oselwero it mzabibu maga,
\q2 kendo ketho yiende ngʼopega.
\q1 Osepoko potgi
\q2 mi owitogi kucho,
\q2 kendo oweyo bedegi kodongʼ rachere.
\b
\q1 
\v 8 Ywaguru ka ukuyo ka dhako ma pod tin ma orwakore gi law kuyo,
\q2 ka oywago chwore mane ohange.
\q1 
\v 9 Chiwo mag cham kod misango miolo piny
\q2 orumo e od Jehova Nyasaye.
\q1 Jodolo ywak
\q2 joma tiyo e nyim Jehova Nyasaye ywak.
\q1 
\v 10 Puothe okethore,
\q2 lowo otwo;
\q1 cham okethore,
\q2 divai manyien orumo,
\q2 mo bende onge.
\b
\q1 
\v 11 Kik ugen gimoro un jopur,
\q2 denguru un jopidh mzabibu,
\q1 beduru mokuyo nikech ngano gi shairi,
\q2 nikech cham mochiek manie puothe okethore.
\q1 
\v 12 Mzabibu osetwo
\q2 kendo ngʼowu osener,
\q1 olemo mongʼinore, gi othidhe kod mapera
\q2 kaachiel gi yiende duto mag puodho osetwo.
\q1 Adier mor mar dhano
\q2 bende oserumo.
\s1 Luong mar lokruok
\q1 
\v 13 Yaye un jodolo, rwakreuru gi pien gugru kuywak;
\q2 denguru kendo gouru nduru,
\q2 un joma tiyo e nyim kendo mar misango.
\q1 Biuru, mondo uywagru otieno duto,
\q2 un joma tiyo e nyim kendo mar misango,
\q1 nikech cham mag misango kod misengini miolo piny,
\q2 onge e od Nyasachwa.
\q1 
\v 14 Landuru lemo gi riyo kech maler
\q2 kendo luonguru chokruok maler.
\q1 Chokuru jodongo
\q2 kod ji duto modakie piny,
\q1 mondo gibi e od Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachu,
\q2 mondo giywagre ne Jehova Nyasaye.
\b
\q1 
\v 15 Mano kaka odiechiengno lich!
\q2 Nimar odiechieng Jehova Nyasaye chiegni,
\q2 enobi kaka kethruok moa kuom Nyasaye Maratego.
\b
\q1 
\v 16 Donge chiemo osegol oko e nyim wangʼwa;
\q2 donge ilo kod mor onge e od Nyasachwa?
\q1 
\v 17 Kothe otop
\q2 motwo ei lowo.
\q1 Ute keno okethore,
\q2 dere osego piny,
\q2 nikech cham onge.
\q1 
\v 18 Mano kaka dhok chur!
\q2 Kweth mag jamni tangni koni gi koni,
\q1 nikech gionge lek;
\q2 kata mana kweth mag rombe sandore.
\b
\q1 
\v 19 In ema aluongi, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 nikech mach osewangʼo pewe mag kwath,
\q2 kendo ligek mach osewangʼo yiende duto manie pap.
\q1 
\v 20 Koda ka le mag thim bende tangni ka dwari nikech
\q2 aore duto oseduono,
\q2 kendo mach osewangʼo pewe mag kwath.
\c 2
\s1 Mony mar bonyo
\q1 
\v 1 Gouru tungʼ e Sayun;
\q2 kendo gouru milome e goda maler.
\b
\q1 Ji duto modak e piny mondo otetni,
\q2 nikech odiechiengʼ mar Jehova Nyasaye biro.
\q1 Osesudo machiegni.
\q2 
\v 2 En odiechiengʼ mar mudho kod kuyo,
\q2 kendo en odiechieng mar rumbi kod mudho mandiwa.
\q1 Ochalo gi piny moyawore ma lerne rieny e kor gode;
\q2 oganda mangʼongo kendo maratego mar jolweny biro,
\q1 mane pok one nyaka nene,
\q2 kendo ok nochak one ndalo mabiro nyaka chiengʼ.
\b
\q1 
\v 3 Mach wengʼo nyimgi,
\q2 to bangʼ-gi ligek mach bebnie.
\q1 Piny chalo gi puoth Eden yo ka nyimgi
\q2 to ka bangʼ-gi piny otwo modongʼ nono,
\q2 onge gimoro manyalo pusorenegi matony.
\q1 
\v 4 Kitgi chalo kaka farese;
\q2 Gilengʼore kaka jolweny moidho farese.
\q1 
\v 5 Gilengʼore ewi gode gi koko machalo koko mag geche lweny,
\q2 kendo kaka mach makakni kawangʼo yugi,
\q1 kendo mana kaka oganda mar jolweny maroteke machanore ne lweny.
\b
\q1 
\v 6 Ka ogendini goyo wangʼni kuomgi,
\q2 to gidhier nono kendo wengegi lil.
\q1 
\v 7 Gibiro ka giger ka jokedo;
\q2 gilwenyo ohinga ka jolweny.
\q1 Gipangore wangʼ achiel ka gichanore,
\q2 ma ok gilok yorgi.
\q1 
\v 8 Ok gituomre, moro ka moro pangore
\q2 kochimo nyime tir.
\q1 Gimuomo gik madigengʼ-gi
\q2 ka ok giketho kaka gichanore.
\q1 
\v 9 Gichomo dala maduongʼ gireto,
\q2 giringo ka gilwenyo ohinga,
\q1 giidho nyaka ei udi;
\q2 kendo gidonjo gie dirisni mana ka jokwoge.
\b
\q1 
\v 10 Piny tetni e nyimgi,
\q2 polo bende yiengni,
\q1 chiengʼ gi dwe lokore mudho,
\q2 to sulwe bende ok rieny.
\q1 
\v 11 Jehova Nyasaye kok matek
\q2 e nyim jolweny mage;
\q1 jolweny mage ok nyal kwan,
\q2 joma winje gin joma roteke.
\q1 Odiechieng Jehova Nyasaye duongʼ;
\q2 kendo olich mokadho.
\q2 En ngʼa manyalo siro odiechiengno?
\s1 Lokuru chunyu
\q1 
\v 12 Jehova Nyasaye owacho ni,
\q2 “Kata sani, dwoguru ira gi chunyu duto,
\q2 ka uriyo kech kendo uywak kendo udengo.”
\b
\q1 
\v 13 Lokuru chunyu,
\q2 to ok lepu.
\q1 Dwoguru ir Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasachu,
\q2 nikech ongʼwon kendo okecho ji,
\q1 iye ok wangʼ piyo kendo ojahera,
\q2 bende chunye lendo kuom kelo ne ji masira kata chwat.
\q1 
\v 14 En ngʼa mongʼeyo? Onyalo lokore mi okechu
\q2 kendo owenu gweth,
\q1 kendo ubed gi chiwo mag cham kod misengini
\q2 miolo piny muchiwo ni Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasachu.
\b
\q1 
\v 15 Gouru turumbete e Sayun,
\q2 landuru lemo mar riyo kech maler,
\q2 luonguru chokruok maler.
\q1 
\v 16 Chokuru ji kanyakla,
\q2 pwodhuru chokruok mar oganda,
\q1 chokuru jodongo kaachiel,
\q2 keluru nyithindo kaachiel,
\q2 koda nyithindo madhodho thuno.
\q1 Wuowi monyombo machiegni mondo owuogi oa e ode,
\q2 kendo miaha mondo owuogi oa kachiena.
\q1 
\v 17 Jodolo, matiyo e nyim Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 mondo oywagi, e kind agola gi
\q2 kendo mar misango mar hekalu.
\q1 Giywag kagiwacho niya, “Yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 kik itiek jogi.
\q1 Kik imi girkeni mari obed gima ichayo,
\q2 ma ogendini wuoyo kuome marach.
\q1 Angʼo ma dimi giwachi e dier ogendini niya,
\q2 ‘Ere Nyasachgi?’ ”
\s1 Dwoko mar Jehova Nyasaye
\q1 
\v 18 Eka Jehova Nyasaye nyiego nomaki
\q2 nikech pinye kendo nokech joge.
\p 
\v 19 Jehova Nyasaye nodwokgi kowacho niya,
\q1 “Abiro miyou cham gi divai manyien kod mo zeituni,
\q2 moromo yiengʼou chuth;
\q1 ok anachak ami ubed
\q2 jogo michayo e dier ogendini.
\b
\q1 
\v 20 “Anariemb jolweny moa nyandwat madhi mabor kodu,
\q2 anariembu nyaka e thim motwo,
\q1 joge motelo nodhi e nam man yo wuok chiengʼ,
\q2 to modongʼ nodhi e nam man yo podho chiengʼ.
\q1 To jogi motho biro dungʼ,
\q2 mi dungʼne nopongʼ piny.”
\b
\q1 Adiera osetimo gik madongo.
\q2 
\v 21 Yaye piny, weuru luor;
\q2 bed mamor kendo moil,
\q1 adiera Jehova Nyasaye osetimo gik madongo.
\q2 
\v 22 Yaye le manie thim, weuru luor;
\q2 nikech pewe kwath koro loth,
\q1 yiende nyago olembegi;
\q2 Ngʼowu gi mzabibu golo mwandugi.
\q1 
\v 23 Yaye jo-Sayun moruru,
\q2 beduru moil kuom Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasachu,
\q1 nikech osemiyou
\q2 koth mar chwiri e yo makare,
\q1 asemiyou ngʼidho mogundho,
\q2 moriwo kodh chwiri kod kodh opon, mana kaka chon.
\q1 
\v 24 Kuonde dino cham nopongʼ gi cham;
\q2 kendo degi nopongʼ mi-oo oko gi divai manyien kod mo.
\b
\q1 
\v 25 “Abiro chulou kuom higni ma bonyo osechamo;
\q2 bonyo madongo gi matindo,
\q2 gi bonyo mamoko gi mony mar bonyo;
\q1 ma gin oganda maduongʼ mar jolweny mara mane aoro e dieru.
\q1 
\v 26 Unubed gi chiemo mathoth, ma uchamo nyaka unuyiengʼ,
\q2 kendo unupak nying Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 ma Nyasachu, mosetimonu timbe miwuoro.
\q1 Wi joga ok nochak okuod kendo.
\q1 
\v 27 Eka unungʼe ni antie ei Israel,
\q2 ni An e Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasachu,
\q1 kendo ni onge moro machielo;
\q2 wi joga ok nochak okuod kendo.”
\s1 Odiechiengʼ mar Jehova Nyasaye
\q1 
\v 28 “Bangʼe,
\q2 anaol Roho Maler mara kuom ji duto.
\q1 Yawuotu gi nyiu nokor wach,
\q2 jodongu nolek lek,
\q2 jou matindo none fweny.
\q1 
\v 29 Kata mana jotichna machwo gi mamon,
\q2 bende, naol Roho Maler mara kuomgi ndalono.
\q1 
\v 30 Anatim honni miwuoro e kor polo
\q2 to e piny,
\q2 remo gi mach kod iro madhwolore nobedie.
\q1 
\v 31 Wangʼ chiengʼ nolokre mudho
\q2 to dwe nolokre remo,
\q2 kapok odiechiengʼ maduongʼ kendo malich mar Jehova Nyasaye ochopo.
\q1 
\v 32 To ngʼato ka ngʼato maluongo
\q2 nying Jehova Nyasaye noresi;
\q1 nikech ewi got Sayun kendo ei Jerusalem
\q2 resruok nobedie,
\q2 mana kaka Jehova Nyasaye osewacho,
\q1 e dier joma otony
\q2 ma Jehova Nyasaye oluongo.”
\c 3
\s1 Ongʼad bura ne pinje
\q1 
\v 1 “E ndalogo kendo e sano,
\q2 ka anadwok ni Juda gi Jerusalem mwandugi mane olalnegi.
\q1 
\v 2 Abiro choko pinje duto
\q2 mi akelgi mwalo e Holo mar paw Jehoshafat.
\q1 Kanyono ema anangʼad nigi e bura,
\q2 kuom girkeni mara, ma gin joga ma jo-Israel,
\q1 nikech negikeyo joga e kind pinje
\q2 kendo gikawo pinya gipogo.
\q1 
\v 3 Negigoyo ombulu kuom joga
\q2 kendo negiloko ohala mar hono yawuowi ka giwilo gi ochode;
\q1 nyiri to negiuso ka giwilo gi divai,
\q2 mondo gimadhi.
\p 
\v 4 “Yaye, jo-Turo gi jo-Sidon, kod joma odak e gwenge mag Filistia, ulawa nangʼo? Koso uchulona kuor nikech gimoro masetimo? Ka uchulona kuor to abiro dwoko timbeu e wiwu uwegi kuom gima usetimo moruyore kendo mapiyo.
\v 5 Nimar usekawo fedha gi dhahabu mara, kendo usedar gi mwanduga mabeyo mogik e hekalu mau.
\v 6 Ne uuso jo-Juda gi Jerusalem ne jo-Yunani, eka utergi mabor gi pinygi mane onywolgie.
\p 
\v 7 “Neuru, abiro wakogi ka agologi kuonde mane uusogie, kendo naket e wiwu uwegi gima usetimo.
\v 8 Abiro miyo jo-Juda ngʼiewo yawuotu, gin to giniusgi ne jo-Sabea, ma en piny mabor miwuoro,” Jehova Nyasaye osewacho.
\q1 
\v 9 Landuru wachni e dier pinje,
\q2 Ikreuru ne lweny!
\q1 Jolweny magu duto oikre ne kedo!
\q2 Jokedo duto mondo osudre machiegni mondo gitug lweny.
\q1 
\v 10 Thedhuru kwe mau olokre ligengni,
\q2 to rabeti mau obed tonge.
\q1 Ngʼat ma ngoro mondo owach niya,
\q2 “An gi teko!”
\q1 
\v 11 Biuru piyo, un ogendini duto moa kuonde duto,
\q2 mondo uchokru kanyo.
\b
\q1 Yaye Jehova Nyasaye kel jokedo magi olor kanyo!
\b
\q1 
\v 12 “Pinje mondo owakre,
\q2 gichom Holo mar Jehoshafat,
\q1 nikech anabed kanyo
\q2 mondo angʼad bura ne pinje duto moa koni gi koni.
\q1 
\v 13 Runduru musmeno,
\q2 nikech cham ochiek.
\q1 Biuru, unyon yiend Zeituni
\q2 nikech kar biyo mzabibu opongʼ,
\q2 kendo degni opongʼ mopukore.
\q1 Mano kaka timbegi maricho dongo!”
\b
\q1 
\v 14 Mano oganda maduongʼ manade, mano kaka gingʼeny
\q2 ka ginie holo ma en kar ngʼado bura!
\q1 Nikech odiechieng Jehova Nyasaye chiegni chopo
\q2 e holo mar ngʼado paro.
\q1 
\v 15 Chiengʼ gi dwe nolokre mudho,
\q2 kendo sulwe ok nochak orieny.
\q1 
\v 16 Jehova Nyasaye noruti koa Sayun
\q2 kendo nomor koa Jerusalem.
\q2 Piny gi Polo noyiengni;
\q1 to Jehova Nyasaye nobed kar pondo mar joge;
\q2 nobed ragengʼ ne jo-Israel.
\s1 Gweth ne jo-Nyasaye
\q1 
\v 17 “Eka unungʼe ni An, Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasachu,
\q2 adak e Sayun, goda maler.
\q1 Jerusalem nobed kama ler,
\q2 ogendini mamoko ok nochak omonje kendo.
\b
\q1 
\v 18 “Odiechiengʼno divai manyien nochwer kawuok ewi gode;
\q2 kendo chak nomol kawuok ewi thuche,
\q2 holo mag pi nopongʼ chuth.
\q1 Soko nomol koa e od Jehova Nyasaye
\q2 kendo pi moaye sokono biro mol e holo mar Shitim.
\q1 
\v 19 Misri nobed piny ma ji odar oweyo,
\q2 kendo Edom nobed piny ongoro maonge tich,
\q1 nikech timbe mahundu mane otimone jo-Juda,
\q2 mane gichweroe remo maonge ketho e pinygi.
\q1 
\v 20 Juda nobed kama ji odakie nyaka chiengʼ
\q2 kendo Jerusalem bende tienge gi tienge.
\q1 
\v 21 Kethogi mar chwero remo mapok aweyonegi,
\q2 abiro weyonegi.”
\b
\qc Jehova Nyasaye odak Sayun!
